prisma_schema:
model Product {
  id           Int     @id
  product_name String? @db.VarChar(255)
  price        Float?
  describe     String? @db.VarChar(255)
}

model User {
  id   Int     @id
  name String? @db.VarChar(255)
  age  Int?
  sex  String? @db.VarChar(255)
}

model comment {
  id        Int    @id @default(autoincrement())
  comments  String
  studen_id Int

  @@index([studen_id], map: "comment_studen_id_fkey")
}

model grade {
  id         Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt  DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt  DateTime
  deletedAt  DateTime?
  score      String
  student_id Int
  student    student   @relation(fields: [student_id], references: [id])

  @@index([student_id], map: "grade_student_id_fkey")
}

model messages {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime
  deletedAt DateTime?
  name      String
  message   String
  payload   Json
}

model question {
  id        Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  question  String
  answer    String
}

model student {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime
  deletedAt DateTime?
  name      String
  grade     grade[]
}

model test0201 {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime
  deletedAt DateTime?
  ceshi     String
}

model test0201001 {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime
  deletedAt DateTime?
  ceshi     String
}

model th_app_type {
  id          Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt   DateTime? @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime?
  deletedAt   DateTime?
  description String
  name        String
}

model todo {
  id           Int       @id @unique @default(autoincrement())
  title        String    @db.VarChar(255)
  user_id      Int
  is_completed Boolean
  is_public    Boolean
  created_at   DateTime? @default(now())

  @@index([user_id], map: "todo_user_id_fkey")
}
